title: #92Noon reacts to the death of Tony Sparano
description: #92Noon reacts to the death of Vikings O-line coach Tony Sparano. Vikings lineman Jeremiah Sirles called in to share his memories of Coach Sparano. Also, The Athletic's Michael Russo talks about the Wild's latest moves, including Matt Dumba's new contract. And LaVelle E. Neal III makes his regular appearance.
